ISLAMABAD, Mar 27 (APP): Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib on Sunday said caravans from all over the country were heading towards Islamabad.
He said PTI workers were on their way to Islamabad and on all highways and motorways, the party flags were seen everywhere. He said today it would be decided who was on the path of truth and uprightness.
